    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has some noticeable scuffs, a few small dings, and the paint is starting to fade on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few minor stains, but all essential features like the heater and radio are fully functional. Mechanically, it runs well enough for commuting, though you should expect the typical maintenance needs of a higher-mileage car. It is a solid, honest vehicle for someone looking for affordable transportation without the frills.",
