    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project? This vehicle is ready for someone with a mechanical touch to bring it back to its former glory! While it currently requires significant repairs and has seen plenty of miles, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for parts. Grab this diamond in the rough at a price that leaves plenty of room for your upgrades!",
